' Gambar (rencana): Sequence diagram — REST K round-trip vs GraphQL 1 round-trip (inti RQ2)
' Notasi: OMG UML 2.5 sequence diagram (lifeline, activation bar/ExecutionSpecification,
'         combined fragment loop, pesan bernomor).
' Basis kode (diverifikasi 2026-07-04):
'   k6/workload_mot.js restIteration() M5/M6, gqlIteration(), apqGet()
'   rest_server.py /tracks/{id}, /tracks/{id}/trajectory
'   graphql_server.py Query.tracks (prefetch), core/dal.py get_track_trajectory /
'   get_tracks_with_trajectories (2 SQL IN-clause total berapa pun K)
' Catatan kejujuran: kedua protokol TIDAK pernah aktif bersamaan (server
' bergantian di port 8000); dua frame di bawah membandingkan dua eksekusi
' terpisah atas halaman K id track yang sama (skenario M6).
@startuml
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName sans-serif
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign left
skinparam ParticipantPadding 12
skinparam BoxPadding 8

title Perbandingan jumlah round-trip: REST (K panggilan) vs GraphQL (1 kueri komposit)\nSkenario M6 — halaman berisi K id track; jaringan lan (delay 5 ms/arah)

participant "k6\n(klien)" as K6
participant "Server REST\n(FastAPI, :8000)" as REST
participant "Server GraphQL\n(Strawberry, :8000)" as GQL
participant "DAL bersama\n(core/dal.py)" as DAL
database "SQLite\nmot_detections.db" as DB

group Eksekusi REST — M6: K round-trip HTTP berurutan (round_trip_count = K)
  autonumber 1 "<b>[R0]"
  loop i = 1..K (setiap id track dalam halaman)
    K6 -> REST : GET /tracks/{id_i}/trajectory?window=2
    activate REST
    REST -> DAL : get_track_trajectory(id_i, window=2)
    activate DAL
    DAL -> DB : SELECT track JOIN class WHERE id = ?
    activate DB
    DB --> DAL : baris track
    deactivate DB
    DAL -> DB : SELECT detection JOIN image\nWHERE track_id = ? AND frame_index BETWEEN ?±W
    activate DB
    DB --> DAL : titik trajektori
    deactivate DB
    DAL --> REST : track + trajectory (dict)
    deactivate DAL
    REST --> K6 : 200 JSON (kompak) + ETag/Cache-Control
    deactivate REST
  end
  note right of K6
    page_latency = Σ durasi K respons
    Biaya jaringan ≈ K × RTT
  end note
end

group Eksekusi GraphQL — M6: 1 round-trip HTTP komposit (round_trip_count = 1)
  autonumber 1 "<b>[G0]"
  K6 -> GQL : GET /graphql?extensions={sha256Hash}\n&variables={ids:[K id]}  (APQ)
  activate GQL
  GQL -> GQL : lookup persisted query\n(registrasi 1× per query, run pertama)
  GQL -> DAL : get_tracks_with_trajectories(ids, window=2)
  activate DAL
  DAL -> DB : SELECT track JOIN class WHERE id IN (K id)
  activate DB
  DB --> DAL : K baris track
  deactivate DB
  DAL -> DB : SELECT detection JOIN image JOIN track\nWHERE track_id IN (K id) AND frame_index BETWEEN first_frame±W
  activate DB
  DB --> DAL : semua titik trajektori
  deactivate DB
  DAL --> GQL : K track + trajectory (batch, urutan = ids)
  deactivate DAL
  GQL --> K6 : 200 {"data":{"tracks":[…K item…]}} + ETag/Cache-Control
  deactivate GQL
  note right of K6
    page_latency = durasi 1 respons
    Biaya jaringan ≈ 1 × RTT
  end note
end

note over K6, DB
  Skenario M5 (trajektori bersarang satu track) mengikuti pola yang sama dengan K = 2 pada sisi REST:
  [1] GET /tracks/{id}  lalu  [2] GET /tracks/{id}/trajectory?center_frame=…&window=W  (round_trip_count = 2),
  sedangkan GraphQL tetap 1 kueri track{…trajectory{…}} (round_trip_count = 1).
end note
@enduml
